    "It can be used to implement FL algorithms, which involve multiple parties training an ML model on their data Results and Analysis of ExperimentsThe experimental data and analyses are presented in this section.",
    "We employed TL to improve accuracy and cut down on training time.",
    "The ImageNet dataset is used to train all DL modules.",
    "The detection accuracy of low-quality videos has increased by varying amounts in different datasets after employing the TL technique, as shown in Table 3, and the detection accuracy of HQ films has increased by 0.4% for the DFDC dataset.",
